  "instructions": [
    "Heat vegetable oil in a large skillet over medium-high heat.",
    "Fry corn tortillas in batches until crispy and golden, about 1-2 minutes per side.",
    "Drain tortillas on paper towels and season with salt, cayenne pepper, and black pepper.",
    "In a separate skillet, warm shredded cheese over low heat, stirring frequently.",
    "To assemble the tacos, place a fried tortilla on a plate and top with warm cheese, diced radishes, and avocado slices.",
    "Squeeze fresh lime juice over the top and sprinkle with cilantro and a pinch of fleur de sel.",
    "Repeat with remaining tortillas and toppings, serving immediately.",
    "Garnish with additional cilantro and radishes, if desired."
  ],
